To avoid the model being overdetermined, as is the case for a lot
of second-generation electrophysiological models (13, 14, 24), we
followed the approach suggested by Hund et al. (24) and accounted
for the external stimulus current (Istim) and the axial current ﬂow (Iax)
in the equation for Ki dynamics. As mentioned above, conductances
of background leakage, plateau, and pump currents were chosen such

